  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Branch Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong></p>\n<p>Shugar Prestige is a premium beauty and nail salon located in the heart of Orchard Road. We are dedicated to delivering exceptional customer service, professional beauty treatments, and a luxurious experience for our clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Overview</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a proactive and customer-oriented Assistant Branch Manager to support daily operations, ensure service quality, and lead our team to achieve business targets. The ideal candidate will have a passion for the beauty and nail industry, strong people management skills, and the ability to create a welcoming environment for both customers and staff.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist the Branch Manager in overseeing daily salon operations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Supervise and motivate staff to achieve service and sales goals</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Manage appointment schedules and ensure smooth workflow</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Handle customer feedback and resolve service issues promptly</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Monitor inventory levels and coordinate product orders</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Maintain cleanliness, hygiene, and service standards in line with company policies</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist in staff training and performance evaluations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Support marketing and promotional activities to drive customer engagement</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Minimum 2 years of experience in beauty, nail, or retail management</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Strong leadership and team management skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Excellent customer service and communication abilities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ability to work retail hours, weekends, and public holidays</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Good organisational skills and attention to detail</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Proficiency in Microsoft Office and basic POS systems</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Experience in beauty/nail services is an advantage</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Competitive salary with performance incentives</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Staff discounts on beauty and nail services</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Career growth opportunities within a premium salon brand</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Supportive and dynamic work environment</p>",
